{"tid":1232532,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"今日遊行既人我估計有半個勞動人口","createTime":"2019-06-16T15:40:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T15:42:24.000Z","uid":35172,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a889b050752f9bcb2fd0da0e14b3b4e9c04e199e","tid":1232532,"uid":35172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:40:45.000Z","msg":"跟據政府統計處既數據<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.statistics.gov.hk/pub/B10100022019MM05B0100.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statistics.gov.hk%2Fpub%2FB10100022019MM05B0100.pdf&d=xNvf4PJMmDX7L7bksShbPtg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=9982e647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.statistics.gov.hk/pub/B10100022019MM05B0100.pdf</a><br />\n香港人口 2018年底有 7482500人，65歲或以上有 17.3%，15歲以下既人有 11.5%，即係係 15-64歲既人有 71.2%，約 5327540人，而家都過2百萬人行緊，仲未計插隊個啲，咁 5327540人既一半即係 2663770人，我估計應該約有半個勞動人口出左黎遊行"},{"pid":"45fd3cfd460df3f97e9f81f6643e434da32263e9","tid":1232532,"uid":4747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:42:24.000Z","msg":"有啲灣仔走，有啲灣仔入，又有啲直去金鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />計埋300萬差唔多"}]}